# Zenith Connect Cursor Rules

Always read AGENTS.md, PROJECT_RULES.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, and SECURITY.md before responding.

## Stack Quick Reference
- Next.js 15 App Router + TypeScript strict
- Supabase @supabase/ssr (NEVER auth-helpers-nextjs)
- Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui
- OpenRouter AI (lib/ai/client.ts)
- Trystero P2P (Nostr)
- Stripe (Checkout + Webhooks)
- Leaflet + OSM (NO MapTiler)
- next-intl i18n

## Non-negotiables
- getAll/setAll cookie pattern only (see lib/supabase/)
- Server components first; 'use client' only when necessary
- All queries through lib/supabase/queries.ts
- Zod validation on ALL user inputs
- RLS on ALL new tables
- Rate-limit all AI and payment endpoints via lib/rate-limit.ts
